Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 放开我
